(n, r) = map(int, input().split())
for i in range(n):
    R = int(input())
    print('Good boi') if R >= r else print('Bad boi')

(N, r) = map(int, input().split())
for _ in range(N):
    R = int(input())
    print('Good boi') if R >= r else print('Bad boi')

(people, r) = map(int, input().split())
while people:
    a = int(input())
    print('Good boi' if a >= r else 'Bad boi')
    people -= 1
